REAME file for MCMC_Break_Stream_Cipher

1. Compile
    > make

2. Execution
    > ./mcmc_stream_cipher [textfilename] [#iteration] [#cycle]

3. Default settings
    (a) Key length
        The default setting of key length is in Makefile. You can freely
        chenge the setting. The default length of key is 128.

4. Demo version
    In the demo version, you can see the original text, the cipher text and
    the recovered text.
    To compile the demo version, just type
        > make demo
    And execute the file just like the previous one.
